84
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,880
The first is changing the copy on the website.

85
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:38,720
So when we revamped our website, the biggest thing is what can this tagline say?

86
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:41,120
As you can see right here, the next generation of pop-ups.

87
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:44,160
And when I click on product, this says pop-up features.

88
00:04:44,160 --> 00:04:48,720
It doesn't say product features because these are only features that exist inside of the pop-up,

89
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,840
which is all that we do.

90
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:51,120
We are the best at pop-ups.

91
