I actually have a bookmark post right here.

97
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,520
We're at 3.5 million AR pop-ups.

98
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,080
That's all we do.

99
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:07,280
Pop-ups equals Alia.

100
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:08,479
Alia equals pop-ups.

101
00:05:08,479 --> 00:05:11,840
So now when people see this, I I I pinned it to my profile.

102
00:05:11,840 --> 00:05:14,320
If someone wants to look me up, this is the first thing they're going to see.

103
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:16,639
