182
00:09:05,839 --> 00:09:07,760
And you should ask yourself those questions.

183
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:11,200
If you have a team, if you have co-founders, do it with your co-founders.

184
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:16,480
Third is try the positioning out on sales calls and see the live reaction of those customers.

185
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:17,839
See if those close more often.

186
00:09:17,839 --> 00:09:21,680
See if they understand the product better and see if they're more excited about it.

