Even if it isn't, you can go back to step two, talk to your co-founders again, go through those questions again,

189
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:34,000
and maybe thinking about a new position that's going to be better.

190
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:34,320
>> All right.

