If you can find the people who are willing to do that with you, make the changes, pivot accordingly,

201
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,440
those are the right people to have.

202
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:17,920
The last question I have for you, Sean, is if you could go back in time, stand on Shawn's shoulders before you found this product market fit before you took this business from basically 0ero to 4 million in the span of about a

